{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <strong>KALAKALA</strong>, a 3D retro cartoon party game set in the depths of hell!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this four-player showdown, pick up your own skull and hurl it at your opponents to score points and defeat your rivals.Show off your skills, dominate various modes and maps, and claim victory with high scores!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3407040/extras/kalala2.png?t=1736108781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Simple controls, easy for everyone to pick up&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No complicated mechanics\u2014just move, jump, and throw. Enjoy the fun of the game with ease!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3407040/extras/kalakala\u622a\u57161.png?t=1736108781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Different modes, unique fun&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game offers two distinct modes for players to choose from, allowing you to play based on your preferences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3407040/extras/03.png?t=1736108781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Fun and varied map mechanics&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each map type features unique interactive elements, offering players different gameplay experiences. For example, in the arena map, floating ghosts can help players attack opponents, while in the alchemy workshop map, teleporters provide opportunities for both attacking and escaping.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3407040/extras/09.png?t=1736108781\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.